---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policies — Katafract"
  description="Katafract apps collect zero data. No servers, no tracking, no accounts. Choose your app to read its full privacy policy."
  ogDescription="All Katafract apps collect zero data. No servers, no tracking, no accounts. Your data stays on your device."
  section="prose"
>
  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  <style slot="head" is:global>

    .app-policy-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
    }
    .app-policy-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(100,100,120,0.14);
      background: rgba(10,10,20,0.4);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }
    .app-policy-card:hover {
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(10,10,20,0.7);
    }
    .app-policy-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 0.875rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      border: 1px solid;
    }
    .app-policy-meta { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
    .app-policy-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #EBF0F7;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }
    .app-policy-desc {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: #8C94A6;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .app-policy-status {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .app-policy-arrow {
      color: #4a5060;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .platform-policy {
      background: rgba(0,240,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }
    .platform-policy h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #EBF0F7;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .platform-policy h2::before { display: none; }
    .zero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .zero-item {
      background: rgba(5,5,15,0.6);
      border: 1px solid rgba(100,100,120,0.12);
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .zero-val {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #00F0FF;
    }
    .zero-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #8C94A6;
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }
  
  </style>


    <div class="prose-header">
      <p class="prose-eyebrow">Katafract</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policies</h1>
      <p class="prose-meta">Katafract LLC &mdash; Last updated April 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-body">

      <div class="callout">
        <p>Every Katafract app is engineered from the ground up to collect nothing. No servers, no accounts, no analytics SDKs. Your data stays on your device &mdash; by design, not by policy alone.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Privacy Policy by App</h2>
      <p>Select your app to read its full privacy policy.</p>

      <div class="app-policy-list">

        <a href="//privacy/safeopen" class="app-policy-card" style="border-color: rgba(0,240,255,0.1);" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,240,255,0.25)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,240,255,0.1)'">
          <div class="app-policy-icon" style="background:rgba(0,240,255,0.05);border-color:rgba(0,240,255,0.2);color:#00F0FF">&#x1F517;</div>
          <div class="app-policy-meta">
            <div class="app-policy-name">SafeOpen</div>
            <div class="app-policy-desc">Free tier is fully on-device. Pro uses a secure backend proxy for AI analysis &mdash; your IP never touches the destination.</div>
          </div>
          <span class="app-policy-status" style="background:rgba(0,240,255,0.1);color:#00F0FF">Live on App Store</span>
          <span class="app-policy-arrow">&#8250;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="//privacy/exifarmor" class="app-policy-card" style="--hover-color: rgba(0,240,255,0.12); border-color: rgba(0,240,255,0.1);" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,240,255,0.25)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,240,255,0.1)'">
          <div class="app-policy-icon" style="background:rgba(0,240,255,0.05);border-color:rgba(0,240,255,0.2);color:#00F0FF">&#x1F6E1;&#xFE0F;</div>
          <div class="app-policy-meta">
            <div class="app-policy-name">ExifArmor</div>
            <div class="app-policy-desc">Photo metadata stripping. No photos, EXIF data, or location ever leaves your device.</div>
          </div>
          <span class="app-policy-status" style="background:rgba(0,240,255,0.1);color:#00F0FF">Live on App Store</span>
          <span class="app-policy-arrow">&#8250;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="//privacy/parkarmor" class="app-policy-card" style="border-color: rgba(74,222,128,0.1);" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(74,222,128,0.25)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(74,222,128,0.1)'">
          <div class="app-policy-icon" style="background:rgba(74,222,128,0.05);border-color:rgba(74,222,128,0.2);color:#4ADE80">&#x1F4CD;</div>
          <div class="app-policy-meta">
            <div class="app-policy-name">ParkArmor</div>
            <div class="app-policy-desc">Parking location saved locally only. No location history, no cloud sync, no accounts.</div>
          </div>
          <span class="app-policy-status" style="background:rgba(74,222,128,0.1);color:#4ADE80">Up Next</span>
          <span class="app-policy-arrow">&#8250;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="//privacy/docarmor" class="app-policy-card" style="border-color: rgba(232,121,249,0.1);" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(232,121,249,0.25)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(232,121,249,0.1)'">
          <div class="app-policy-icon" style="background:rgba(232,121,249,0.05);border-color:rgba(232,121,249,0.2);color:#E879F9">&#x1F510;</div>
          <div class="app-policy-meta">
            <div class="app-policy-name">DocArmor</div>
            <div class="app-policy-desc">AES-256 encrypted document vault. Face ID protected. iCloud sync explicitly disabled.</div>
          </div>
          <span class="app-policy-status" style="background:rgba(100,100,120,0.1);color:#8C94A6">Planned</span>
          <span class="app-policy-arrow">&#8250;</span>
        </a>

      </div>

      <div class="platform-policy">
        <h2>Platform-Wide Commitments</h2>
        <p style="color:#8C94A6;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:0">These commitments apply across all Katafract apps. Where an app&rsquo;s Pro tier requires backend processing (such as SafeOpen&rsquo;s proxy and AI analysis), that processing is explicitly disclosed in the app&rsquo;s individual privacy policy below &mdash; and is designed to protect your identity, not compromise it.</p>
        <div class="zero-grid">
          <div class="zero-item"><div class="zero-val">Zero</div><div class="zero-label">personal data collected</div></div>
          <div class="zero-item"><div class="zero-val">Zero</div><div class="zero-label">cloud accounts required</div></div>
          <div class="zero-item"><div class="zero-val">Zero</div><div class="zero-label">analytics SDKs</div></div>
          <div class="zero-item"><div class="zero-val">Zero</div><div class="zero-label">advertising trackers</div></div>
          <div class="zero-item"><div class="zero-val">Zero</div><div class="zero-label">data sold or shared</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Apple Platform Privacy</h2>
      <p>All Katafract apps are published on the Apple App Store with an Apple Privacy Nutrition Label declaring <strong>Data Not Collected</strong>. We submit these labels accurately and update them if the app's data practices ever change.</p>
      <p>In-app purchases across all apps are processed by Apple via StoreKit. We do not receive your Apple ID, payment method, or billing details for any transaction.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about how any Katafract app handles your data:</p>
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>Privacy Inquiries</h3>
        <p>Katafract LLC</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:privacy@katafract.com">privacy@katafract.com</a></p>
        <p>We typically respond within one business day.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  
</Base>
